preds: ['', 'The hotel has a rooftop pool.', 'The hotel has nightly activities, like a "mixology" presentation at the bar. There\'s nightly stargazing on one of the lawns with a telescope and professional guide. On Saturday night they had a "dive in movie" in the spa pool (it was "Frozen").', '', 'The hotel has an outdoor spring/summer space.', '', '', '', 'The hotel has a dock across the street at their sister property on the I tercoadtal (and they even loan fishing gear).', 'The hotel has scavenger hunts, ranger wildlife lessons, and free chocolate.', 'The hotel has photos in the hallway of the original orphanage.', '', 'The hotel has a sheep and 3 goats.', '', '']
labels: [[''], [''], ['The hotel gives access to a waterslide, free use of the driving range and putting greens with a bag of clubs, mountain bikes and helmets. There are also lots of nightly activities. There\'s nightly stargazing on one of the lawns with a telescope and professional guide. One Saturday night they also had a "dive in movie" in the spa pool. They showed Frozen movie.'], [''], [''], [''], [''], ['The hotel offers coloring books and crayons to occupy kids.'], ['The hotel is on St. Pete Beach. They have a shuffleboard, games, toys, mini-mini golf course, etc. They have a library.'], ['The hotel has hikes for all abilities. They have scavenger hunts, ranger wildlife lessons for kids. They have bocce ball, mini golf, ping pong, arcade, mini museum. They have a tortoise.'], [''], ['Customers can play corn-hole, ping pong, rent jets. Customers can bring their rods and go fishing in a little area. There is an ATM available. They have a store.'], ['The hotel has a sheep and 3 goats who loved to be scratched.'], ['The hotel is on the beach. They have a huge water slide, plenty of paddle boats, free mini golf, chess with jumbo pieces, big trampoline for the kids. A room has a direct view of the beach.'], ['']]
